All 455 tests pass.
Three bugs fixed in `inflection/__init__.py`:

1. **`pluralize` (line 29)**: Changed `r'\1ys'` → `r'\1ies'` so words ending in consonant+y (e.g., `category`, `query`) correctly become `categories`, `queries` instead of `categorys`, `querys`.

2. **`camelize` (line 169)**: Changed `m.group(1).lower()` → `m.group(1).upper()` so that letters after `_` or at the start are capitalized (e.g., `product` → `Product`, `special_guest` → `SpecialGuest`).

3. **`ordinal` (line 229)**: Changed `number % 10` → `number % 100` so that 11, 12, 13 (and negative versions) correctly get `th` suffix instead of `st`/`nd`/`rd`.
