All 455 tests pass. Here's a summary of the three bugs fixed in `inflection/__init__.py`:

1. **`pluralize` (line 29)** — `-y` words were being pluralized as `categorys` instead of `categories`. Changed replacement from `r'\1ys'` to `r'\1ies'`.

