Three bugs fixed in `inflection/__init__.py`:

1. **Plural y-rule** (line 29): `\1ys` → `\1ies` — was emitting `categorys` instead of `categories`
2. **Camelize** (line 169): `m.group(1).lower()` → `m.group(1).upper()` — was lowercasing the first letter instead of capitalizing it
3. **Ordinal** (line 229): `number % 10` → `number % 100` — the exception check for 11th/12th/13th was checking the last digit (1,2,3) instead of the last two digits (11,12,13)
