- `subtotal` → `item_total` (TaxedMoney object → string price)
- `shippingPrice` → `delivery_total` (TaxedMoney object → string price)
- `user` → `customer_id` (User object → customer ID)
- `channel` → `channel_id` (Channel object → channel ID)

**Structural mappings (5)**: Composite objects requiring sub-mapping
- `billingAddress` → `billing_address` (Address objects)
