I've identified all three bugs:

1. **`camelize`** (line 169): `m.group(1).lower()` should be `.upper()` — it lowercases when it should uppercase
2. **`pluralize` rule** (line 29): replacement `r'\1ys'` should be `r'\1ies'` — "category" → "categorys" instead of "categories"
